  The Osun State Government has dropped its case against a young man, who was earlier arrested over a post on Facebook. Governor Gboyega Oyetola directed the Attorney-General and Commissioner for Justice in the state, Femi Akande, and Ministry of Justice to discontinue the trial of Zirhid Akinloye.Â 



